text: Guillermo Rodríguez may refer to: *Guillermo Rodríguez (baseball), Venezuelan baseball catcher *Guillermo Rodríguez (footballer), Uruguayan footballer *Guillermo Rodríguez (athlete), Mexican Olympic sprinter *Guillermo Rodríguez (politician), also known as Guillermo Rodríguez Lara, Ecuadorian politician *Guillermo Rodríguez González, Spanish archer *Guillermo Rodriguez (comedian), Recurring cast member of Jimmy Kimmel Live! *Guillermo Rodríguez Melgarejo, Argentine Roman Catholic bishop
